CARIPARO MBS vs control

Accuracy Palsy

Thomas Quettier

2023-05-16

0.1 Accuracy

For the accuracy responses, we fit generalized linear models (glmer), using lme4 R package (v.1.1-33; Douglas & al. (2023)).We regressed participants’ correct responses (1 = success, 0 = error ) on these sets of regressors [correct ∼ emotion * group * video_set + (1 |ID)]

0.2 Satistics

0.2.1 Correct ~ palsy + (1|subject)

‘palsy’ is computed as follow: mean of Sunnybrook muscle evaluation score when involved in the action units related to a specific emotion. Score range from 0: no movement to 5: complete movement.A 5 default score was added to control group participants.
